title: Keller, Schmid, Myernick enter National Soccer Hall of Fame
text:
> Sports Keller, Schmid, Myernick enter National Soccer Hall of Fame Seattle Sounders FC Head Coach Sigi Schmid hugs retired Sounders goalkeeper Kasey Keller at the National Soccer Hall of Fame induction ceremony at the Museum of History and Industry, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Seattle, Wash. Keller was also inducted into the hall of fame. (Sy Bean/The Seattle Times via AP)
